column1: Results for Cell Block Classic Murfreesboro, Tn. 12/06/08  Powerlifting

Money went to: 1st. Place: Greg Panora - 1000.00 2nd. Place: Luke Edwards - 500.00 3rd. Place: Tony Romas - 250.00  The SPF and Brent Tracey want to thank everyone for coming out and taking part in this event. All of you lifters done a great job and it was an honor to meet each and everyone of you. This was our first Pro Meet, but won't be our last.  We also want to thank Louie Simmons and Mike Ferguson for all there help in bringing this meet together. It was great to meet you both and the meet was a blast, to say the least.
